                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-450-18560407 t18560407-450-punishment-53"></join>Confined Six Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">FOX</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
